{
    "name": "vim.diagnostic.JumpOpts",
    "documentation": [
        "```lua",
        "(class) vim.diagnostic.JumpOpts",
        "```",
        "",
        "---",
        "",
        " Configuration table with the keys listed below. Some parameters can have their default values",
